Basic.Name: Hotshot
Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 210% damage + apply **Bleed** for 2 turns.

Special.Name: Heating Up
Special.Description:
Gain +2 **Offense Up**, up to a maximum of 5.
Apply +1 **Offense Up**, up to a maximum of 3, to all **Fantastic Four** or **Namor** allies.

Ultimate.Name: Supernova
Ultimate.Description:
Attack all enemies for 400% damage. Apply **Offense Down** to all enemies.
This attack is Unavoidable and cannot be countered.

Passive.Name: Flame On!
Passive.Description:
On turn, flip 2 negative effects on self to positive effects.
Gain +30% damage. **Fantastic Four** and **Namor** allies gain +30% damage.
Gain +10000% resistance against **Bleed**.

Basic.Name: Tensile Strength
Basic.Description:
Attack primary target for 230% damage. Chain to 3 adjacent targets for 190% damage.
Counter attack breaks this Chain.

Special.Name: Entangle
Special.Description: Attack primary target for 400% damage + apply **Stun**.

Ultimate.Name: Orbital Assault
Ultimate.Description:
Clear Defense Up from primary target.
Attack primary target for 450% damage.
Gain +100000% Extra Focus for this attack.

Passive.Name: For Science!
Passive.Description:
Gain +20% Resistance. **Fantastic Four** and **Namor** allies gain +20% Resistance.
Gain +20% Focus. **Fantastic Four** and **Namor** allies gain +20% Focus.
On self and each **Fantastic Four** ally's turn, 100% chance to apply **Assist Now** to self, **Namor**, or a random **Fantastic Four** ally. If **Assist Now** is applied, clear **Blind** on that target.
On Turn, choose 3 random enemies. If they have a positive effect, remove 1.

Basic.Name: Neptune's Trident
Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 210% damage + 50% Piercing.

Special.Name: Tidal Wave
Special.Description:
Attack primary target for 350% damage. Attack adjacent targets for 340% damage.
On target Block, Bonus Attack 2 times for 100% Piercing to primary and adjacent targets.

Ultimate.Name: Giganto
Ultimate.Description:
Attack all enemies for 300% damage.
On **War Offense**:
> This attack always Crits
> Clear all positive effects from each target
> Change Speed Bar of all targets by -50%
This attack is Unavoidable and cannot be Countered.

Passive.Name: Imperius Rex
Passive.Description:
Gain +20% damage.
Gain +30% armor.
On **War Offense**:
> On Spawn, apply **Offense Up** for 2 turns to all **Fantastic Four** allies and self.
> On Spawn, apply **Deflect** for 2 turns to all **Fantastic Four** allies or self.
> Gain additional +30% Damage.
> **Fantastic Four** allies gain+30% Damage.

Special.Name: Pummeling Stone
Special.Description: Attack primary target for 280% damage. Bonus Attack 2 times for 220% damage.

Passive.Name: It's Clobberin' Time
Passive.Description:
When attacked, attack that enemy for 150% damage.
Gain +20% Armor. **Fantastic Four** and **Namor** allies gain +20% Armor.

Basic.Name: Submachine Gun
Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 160% damage + apply **Bleed**.

Special.Name: Hyperdose
Special.Description: Gain **Speed Up** for 4 turns + **Heal Block** for 2 turns. Fill Speed Bar by 60%.

Basic.Name: Puncture
Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 270% damage. Pass any negative effects on this character to target. 70% chance to apply **Offense Down**, **Defense Down**, or **Slow** to target.

Special.Name: Biohazard
Special.Description: Gain 3 random negative effects for 2 turns. Heal self for 10000 Health + 20% of Max Health.

Basic.Name: Bash
Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 280% damage. Apply **Defense Down** for 1 turn.

Special.Name: Sudden Evolution
Special.Description: Gain **Offense Up** for 3 turns + **Defense Down** for 2 turns. Heal self for 3000 Health + 5% of Max Health.

Passive.Name: Growth Spurt
Passive.Description: On Turn, 50% chance to Heal for 10% of Max Health.
